[{"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/92cc/2275/92_large.png?m=1582875070", "name": "chrome", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/92cc/2275/92_normal.png?m=1582875070", "title": "Chrome", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/chrome", "topics": 2113, "footer": "", "header": "Google Chrome is a browser that combines a minimal design with sophisticated technology to make the web faster, safer, and easier.", "title_alternative": "Chrome", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/92cc/2275/92_mini.png?m=1582875070", "stars": 1085, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 92, "parent_node_name": "browsers"}, "member": {"id": 468685, "username": "RiverRay", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/RiverRay", "website": "https://leizhenpeng.com", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "leizhenpeng", "btc": "", "location": "武汉", "tagline": "I wish my life to be more than just lengthy. 我希望我的生命不仅仅是漫长", "bio": "拿着奇绩的几百万围绕GPTs Action创业\r\n分享开发者的日常生活哈哈", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a0e8/7713/468685_mini.png?m=1720571984", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a0e8/7713/468685_normal.png?m=1720571984", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a0e8/7713/468685_large.png?m=1720571984", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a0e8/7713/468685_xlarge.png?m=1720571984", "created": 1581345441, "last_modified": 1720571984}, "last_reply_by": "mayli", "last_touched": 1720624603, "title": "一个反常识： 在 Chrome 浏览器里如何拿到用户最真实的 CPU 和其他硬件信息（不走 UA", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1056113", "created": 1720572572, "deleted": 0, "content": "前端老鸟都知道一个常识\r\n\r\n谷歌浏览器里面是拿不到真实 CPU 和硬件信息的\r\n\r\n（：UA 那个很容易伪造好吧\r\n\r\n今天再给你一个反常识：\r\n\r\n其实，Chromium 内置了一个系统级插件。\r\n\r\n这个插件允许 *.google.com 网站获取宿主机 CPU 信息\r\n\r\n去 Chromium 源码里找找，发现插件 ID 是：nkeimhogjdpnpccoofpliimaahmaaome 。\r\n\r\n而且，这个插件还能对外通信\r\n\r\nso ，骚操作来了\r\n\r\n我们可以随便打开一个 Google 的网站在 console 里面输入：\r\n\r\n```\r\nchrome.runtime.sendMessage('nkeimhogjdpnpccoofpliimaahmaaome',\r\n{method: 'cpu.getInfo'},\r\nresponse => console.table(response));\r\n```\r\n![]( https://i.imgur.com/s8z3w0B.png)\r\nCPU 、进程还有负载 一五一十的就有了\r\n\r\n看源代码，这个内置插件里面还暴露了不少其他方法，可以自己探索玩玩\r\n\r\n![]( https://i.imgur.com/PKMFgY2.png)\r\n\r\n说人话：\r\n\r\n如果你做的是浏览器扩展，完全可以获取到宿主机的 CPU 还有其他硬件信息的\r\n\r\n哈哈哈哈哈", "content_rendered": "<p>前端老鸟都知道一个常识</p>\n<p>谷歌浏览器里面是拿不到真实 CPU 和硬件信息的</p>\n<p>（：UA 那个很容易伪造好吧</p>\n<p>今天再给你一个反常识：</p>\n<p>其实，Chromium 内置了一个系统级插件。</p>\n<p>这个插件允许 *.google.com 网站获取宿主机 CPU 信息</p>\n<p>去 Chromium 源码里找找，发现插件 ID 是：nkeimhogjdpnpccoofpliimaahmaaome 。</p>\n<p>而且，这个插件还能对外通信</p>\n<p>so ，骚操作来了</p>\n<p>我们可以随便打开一个 Google 的网站在 console 里面输入：</p>\n<pre><code>chrome.runtime.sendMessage('nkeimhogjdpnpccoofpliimaahmaaome',\n{method: 'cpu.getInfo'},\nresponse =&gt; console.table(response));\n</code></pre>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/s8z3w0B.png\"/>\nCPU 、进程还有负载 一五一十的就有了</p>\n<p>看源代码，这个内置插件里面还暴露了不少其他方法，可以自己探索玩玩</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/PKMFgY2.png\"/></p>\n<p>说人话：</p>\n<p>如果你做的是浏览器扩展，完全可以获取到宿主机的 CPU 还有其他硬件信息的</p>\n<p>哈哈哈哈哈</p>\n", "last_modified": 1720608599, "replies": 138, "id": 1056113}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/dc56/8979/804_large.png?m=1643850384", "name": "mmm", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/dc56/8979/804_normal.png?m=1643850384", "title": "买买买", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/mmm", "topics": 838, "footer": "", "header": "如果你最近买了某个有点点奢侈，但是又非常酷的东西，那就发到这个节点来交（xia）流（du）一下吧", "title_alternative": "Buy Buy Buy", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/dc56/8979/804_mini.png?m=1643850384", "stars": 439, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 804, "parent_node_name": "internet"}, "member": {"id": 361767, "username": "Bigbelly", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Bigbelly", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location